text: Alimami Gory (born 30 August 1996) is a French professional footballer who plays as a striker for Belgian club Cercle Brugge. Gory is of Malian descent. ==Club career== Gory is a youth exponent from Le Havre AC. He made his first team debut on 12 August 2016 against Gazélec Ajaccio replacing Ghislain Gimbert after 70 minutes. ==International career== In October 2018 he received his first call-up to the Mali senior national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:French footballers Category:French expatriate footballers Category:French people of Malian descent Category:Association football forwards Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Belgian First Division A players Category:Le Havre AC players Category:Cercle Brugge K.S.V. players Category:Expatriate footballers in Belgium
